              </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <h3 id="what-you-do-with-your-pension-pot-when-youre-70">What you do with your
              pension pot when you’re 70</h3>

            <p>Your pension pot has grown at 5% a year to £125,000 in the 5 years you left
              it untouched. You decide to take 25% tax free and re-invest the rest. </p>

            <table>
              <thead>
